      "content": "i get that, but it's just such a waste. like, the inflammation is literally gone. my friend said that if you stop as soon as the symptoms disappear, it actually helps prevent antibiotic resistance because you aren't overusing them. if there's no infection left to fight, isn't it better to just stop and not overdo it?",
